 * "Decoding Reed-Solomon Codes"</a> (see discussion of Forney's Formula)</li>
 * <li>J.I. Hall. <a href="www.mth.msu.edu/~jhall/classes/codenotes/GRS.pdf">
 * "Chapter 5. Generalized Reed-Solomon Codes"</a>
